  "detailed_description": "Flex your strategic mastery in <strong>Rogue Citadel</strong>, a fusion of <strong>tower defence</strong> and <strong>survivors</strong> gameplay set within the foreboding Castle Shadowfell. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Battle your way through the <strong>procedurally generated</strong> layers of the castle, adapting your defences to hold off waves of varied horrors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survivors-style Gameplay</h2>Ancient and often bizarre heroes guide you through your adventure, granting you their unique and powerful abilities.<br><br>Build up your hero with carefully chosen upgrades and equipment, gaining in power between runs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=498 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deckbuilding Tower Defence</h2>Construct your deck of defences to keep you and your resources safe as you delve deeper into the Castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Levels</h2>Every level has a unique layout where scouting and placement of your defences will be key.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=498 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play the demo now to check out an early version of the gameplay, and join our Discord channel to discuss your adventures!",
  "about_the_game": "Flex your strategic mastery in <strong>Rogue Citadel</strong>, a fusion of <strong>tower defence</strong> and <strong>survivors</strong> gameplay set within the foreboding Castle Shadowfell. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/9bd437d0e457413c145ed4f2c6f6ee1e.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Battle your way through the <strong>procedurally generated</strong> layers of the castle, adapting your defences to hold off waves of varied horrors.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=298 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/bcba75a86193e0635152b0eb5588d772.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Survivors-style Gameplay</h2>Ancient and often bizarre heroes guide you through your adventure, granting you their unique and powerful abilities.<br><br>Build up your hero with carefully chosen upgrades and equipment, gaining in power between runs.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=498 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1c17a1942505cac9842f8b23e490033e.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Deckbuilding Tower Defence</h2>Construct your deck of defences to keep you and your resources safe as you delve deeper into the Castle.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=500 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/1ec9d3c2a40ae74d8d31217e9185a63c.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Procedural Levels</h2>Every level has a unique layout where scouting and placement of your defences will be key.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.poster.avif?t=1727376496\" width=498 height=306 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.webm?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2782540/extras/8eb3cbc093899bdf0b18e37f428b8f99.mp4?t=1727376496\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Play the demo now to check out an early version of the gameplay, and join our Discord channel to discuss your adventures!",
